<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>404 Page Not Found | POS-BMS</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <style>
        .error-container {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            background-color: #f3f4f6;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .error-code {
            font-size: 120px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #4f46e5;
            margin: 0;
            line-height: 1;
        }
        .error-message {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #1f2937;
            margin: 10px 0 30px 0;
        }
        .error-sub {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #6b7280;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="error-container">
        <h1 class="error-code">404</h1>
        <div class="error-message">Page Not Found / পেজ পাওয়া যায়নি</div>
        <p class="error-sub">Sorry, the page you are looking for does not exist or has been moved.<br>দুঃখিত, আপনি যে পেজটি খুঁজছেন সেটি অস্তিত্বে নেই অথবা সরানো হয়েছে।</p>
        
        <div style="display: flex; gap: 15px;">
            <% if (user) { %>
                <a href="/dashboard" class="btn btn-primary" style="padding: 12px 24px; font-size: 16px;">
                    Go to Dashboard / ড্যাশবোর্ডে যান
                </a>
            <% } else { %>
                <a href="/login" class="btn btn-primary" style="padding: 12px 24px; font-size: 16px;">
                    Go to Login / লগইনে যান
                </a>
            <% } %>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
